text: DC League of Super-Pets is a 2022 American computer-animated superhero comedy movie by Warner Animation Group. It is based on the DC Comics superhero team Legion of Super-Pets. The movie is directed by Jared Stern. The cast includes Dwayne Johnson, Kevin Hart, Kate McKinnon, John Krasinski, Vanessa Bayer, Natasha Lyonne, Diego Luna, Thomas Middleditch, Ben Schwartz, and Keanu Reeves. DC League of Super-Pets was released in the United States on July 29, 2022, by Warner Bros. Pictures.
